    "updated_at": "2024-05-24T14:30:38Z",
    "body": "The homebrew package is updated automatically on every release by uses and could be considered to be maintained by the project. Nevertheless, I checked, and it looks like it's only used to prevent local configs from being picked up when running tests.\r\n\r\nClosing this since the initial issue was addressed.",
