    "updated_at": "2025-03-04T07:53:47Z",
    "body": "I had the same issue, but `starship config command_timeout 3600` resolved it.\n\nI did not get the error message, at the beginning, despite I make commits with Git more than once per week. Suddenly, this error message started to appear all the times I changed directory to one containing a Git repository. (I started to use Starship in January, 2025.)",
